    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all seats remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely require some maintenance soon, such as new tires and a brake service, to ensure long-term reliability. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen it up.",
