      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and absolutely perfect for your daily commute or fun weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right now. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
