    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under load. The drivetrain remains tight, utilizing the Variable M Differential Lock for precise power delivery out of corners. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, offering the communicative feedback and balanced handling characteristic of this chassis. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car with a clean service history, ready for the enthusiast who values performance over a showroom finish.",
