    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 2019 Lexus RX 350 is a meticulously maintained example of luxury and dependability. The Atomic Silver exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by 20-inch split-five-spoke alloy wheels. While the body is remarkably straight, there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the Parchment leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, and the genuine wood trim is devoid of sun-fading or cracks. Every amenity, from the heated/ventilated seats to the premium 12-speaker sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is sound; it has been serviced exclusively at the dealership, with a fresh oil change and a recent multi-point inspection. The tires offer plenty of life, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept SUV that drives as smoothly as the day it was first driven off the lot, showing only the lightest signs of careful previous ownership.",
